    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Beginning at 13th level, against your best efforts, you are a risk-taker at heart and you have a tendency to gamble even when you don't have to. When you make an attack roll, a contested ability check, or saving throw you may choose to make it at disadvantage.</p><p>When you do so, you automatically gain a <em><strong>Dogma</strong></em> and gain advantage on the next attack roll, ability check, or saving throw you make.</p>",
